a band synthesizer that performs a band synthesis on a cross correlation result of each frequency band which is provided by said cross correlation processor;
a long-time integrator that integrates a band synthesis result provided by said band synthesizer for a long time; and
a target detector that detects said target on a basis of an integration result provided by said long-time integrator.
